{{Quote|[&hellip;]and now I believe it is time for us to see Commandant Deenlark.|[[Lieutenant]] [[Mitth'raw'nuruodo|Thrawn]], to [[Imperial cadet|cadet]] [[Eli N. Vanto|Eli Vanto]] after they were attacked|<ref name="Thrawn 1">[[Thrawn 1|''Thrawn'' 1]]</ref>}}
'''Commandant''' was a title given to [[overseer]]s<ref name="Citadel Rescue" /> and [[commanding officer]]s of particular military forces<ref name="The Eye">{{Andor|The Eye}}</ref> or installations, such as [[prison]] camps,<ref name="Citadel Rescue" /> [[Imperial Academy|Imperial Academies]],<ref name="Edge of the Galaxy" /> or [[garrison]]s.<ref name="The Eye" />

During the [[Clone Wars]], [[Osi Sobeck]] was a commandant in the [[Confederacy of Independent Systems]] who served as the [[warden]] of the [[Citadel]], a major prison located on the [[planet]] [[Lola Sayu]].<ref name="Citadel Rescue" /> Toward the end of the [[Galactic Civil War]], [[Camp Sardo]]'s labor facilities in [[Kashyyyk]]'s [[Imperial territory G5-623]] were run by Commandant [[Theodane Sardo]]. Imperial Commadandant [[Stradd]] was captured by [[Norra Wexley]]'s [[Imperial hunter]]s around the same [[time]].<ref name="Life Debt" />

In [[5 BBY]], [[Jayhold Beehaz]], an officer of the [[Imperial Army]], was stationed on [[Aldhani]] and acted as the Commandant of the [[Aldhani Garrison]], overseeing both the [[Aldhani dam]] and the [[Alkenzi Air Base]].<ref name="The Eye">{{Andor|The Eye}}</ref>

The president of the [[Royal Imperial Academy]] on [[Coruscant]] in the [[Galactic Empire]]'s early years was Commandant [[Deenlark]].<ref name="Lost Stars">''[[Lost Stars]]''</ref> [[Cumberlayne Aresko]] carried the title in his duties as an [[officer]] at the Imperial Academy on [[Lothal]], the [[Academy for Young Imperials]].<ref name="Edge of the Galaxy" /> [[Brendol Hux]], overseer of the [[Arkanis Academy]], also carried the title and established a secretive group known as the [[Commandant's Cadets]].<ref name="TSA">''[[Servants of the Empire: The Secret Academy]]''</ref> Hux retained his title of commandant as part of an Imperial remnant on the [[Shadow Council (Imperial Remnants)|Shadow Council]].<ref name="Mando 23">{{TheMandalorian|Chapter 23: The Spies}}</ref>

